name: Gail...🍀🇺🇸
tweet: After 3 yrs,of trying to build trust & trying to save this poor boy from a life of hell,this is a happy ending. This is a prime example of why you should spay & neuter!Why you shouldn't dump your animals on "nice" people!He's now part of our family!Hunter is home! #HuntersJourney pic.twitter.com/ZuPhoziHv8

name: Gail...🍀🇺🇸
tweet: 3 months passed by. I thought of him often. Maybe he found a home? Maybe something bad happened to him? Low & behold I heard a scratch at the door on Thanksgiving. I opened the door to a wonderful surprise! Hunter had come back! He was neutered that week. #HuntersJourney 11/2019 pic.twitter.com/vd8nihEqrR

name: Gail...🍀🇺🇸
tweet: Every month he would come to see me. I would check the cat trap but to no avail. It was now mid August, & CA temps sore to 106°,so I kept water out & there was always cool grass & shade for him to lay in. It would be awhile before I'd see him again... 8/2019 #HuntersJourney pic.twitter.com/DcYo97rXef

name: Gail...🍀🇺🇸
tweet: We finally had our 1st touch on 4th of July weekend. He was flirting with me & I knew after 2.5 years he wasn't a feral. He was abused & then abandoned. He wanted,so badly,to be loved. So we climbed our 1st hurdle. TRUST! 7/3/2019 #HuntersJourney pic.twitter.com/OaBvQkBlF3

name: Gail...🍀🇺🇸
tweet: A month passed by & Alley brought a friend home for dinner. Low & below it was Hunter! He would get just close enough but I still couldn't pet him. But we had gained some trust. The Gang had accepted him. That was a huge step for this abused cat. 6/2019 #HuntersJourney pic.twitter.com/AwPoFdKTTg

name: Gail...🍀🇺🇸
tweet: 3 months passed & we had another sighting. We set the cat trap in the neighbors yard near our the driveway but still no luck. He was so thin but we kept water out near the trap. I was worried but determined to catch him. 5/2019 #HuntersJourney pic.twitter.com/GN53ufKb91

name: Gail...🍀🇺🇸
tweet: Sadly, & ironically,Happy Boy vanished into thin air a month later. But Hunter remained. Happy Boy was the same age Hunter was when Hunter came her as a kitten in 2017. It gives me hope he'll return someday. I really believe he's Hunter's son...💔 5/2019 #HuntersJourney pic.twitter.com/V5mvkHArEz

name: Gail...🍀🇺🇸
tweet: After 1.5 years Hunter was back. He brought this kitten with him. It was strange to see this kitten fondling Hunter & he didn't seem to care? That's unusual w/ makes. So we neutered Happy Boy & set the cat traps again. But still no luck. He was tired. 3/27/19 #HuntersJourney pic.twitter.com/iyXRLLz7a7

name: Gail...🍀🇺🇸
tweet: 1.5 years passed by & still no Hunter?Then a 5mo kitten showed up 1 day out of nowhere,starving to death.We named him Happy Boy. He was unusually friendly with the other cats.The next picture shocked the hell out of me.Guess who came w/ this sweet boy? 3/17/19 #HuntersJourney pic.twitter.com/rotWQxSrpp

name: Gail...🍀🇺🇸
tweet: 8 months went by with no sign of Hunter anywhere. We searched for weeks but had no luck until one day I came home from work & this was the last video I would take for a longtime. He simply vanished again. 8/11/17 #HuntersJourney pic.twitter.com/6EEq4NfiOO

name: Gail...🍀🇺🇸
tweet: Day #10.. I caught a glimpse of Hunter in the meadow across from my house. I decided to set the cat trap there but still no luck! You can barely see him...👇 1/30/17 #HuntersJourney pic.twitter.com/PFC8FHTCzl

name: Gail...🍀🇺🇸
